To Release
----------

Prerequisities:
libdevel-cover-perl libtemplate-perl libtest-pod-coverage-perl libppi-html-perl
libhtml-parser-perl

cpanm XML::Entities

(Notes.)

Commit all changes.

Run tests:
for t in t/*.t; do
  perl -Ilib "$t"
done

Bump version in:
	Writer.pm
	Writer/Encoding.pm

Update changelog.

git commit -a

Locally,

# Create a distribution from the tag
minil release

# Generate coverage report for the new release
perl Build.PL
cover -test -report Html_basic -outputdir coverage

Upload to CPAN.

Update web page:
mkdir temp-website

cd web
./gen-index.pl >../temp-website/index.html
cp style.css ../temp-website/
cd ..

cp -pr coverage temp-website/

cd temp-website
git init
git add .
git commit -m 'Generated website.'

git push -f git@github.com:josephw/xml-writer-perl.git master:refs/heads/gh-pages
